SIMPLE: unclothed
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unclothed
<hw>Un*clothed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<ety>[Properly p. p. of <ets>unclothe</ets>.]</ety> <def>Divested or
stripped of clothing.</def> <rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>clothed</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not yet clothed; wanting clothes;
naked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*cloth"ed*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncloud</ent>⟦br⟧
